      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i dont even see the point anymore. everything is just atoms and entropy. there's no grand design or some higher meaning waiting for us. it's just a long, cold stretch of nothingness until we eventually stop. it feels so heavy knowing that nothing we do actually matters in the end.",
